additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Anionic and Nonionic Surfactants, Oxygen Disingectant, Sodium Aluminosilicate, Sodium Carbonate, Sodium Silicate, Soil Suspending Agent, Antifoam, Perfume

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Caution For medical advice, contact a Poisons Information Centre on 13 11 26 or a doctor. Keep out of reach of children. Use only as directed. Hand Skin Care: After use, rinse and dry hands thoroughly. If skin is sensitive or damaged, avoid contact with the product or wash solution. If in doubt, wear protective gloves. If Swallowed: Wash mouth out with water and then drink a glass of water slowly. Seek medical advice. Eye Contact: Immediately flush with water for at least 15 minutes and seek medical advice.
